        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\n(6 comments)\n\nI did not read everything in detail and I'm not fluent in Robot anyway, so don't take my comments as any way complete. Many of the comments are more like further development suggestions than something that needs to be corrected right now.\n\nI still put -1 as I would really like a brief document (readme-like or if there is Robot standard way then that) included to explain the relationship with SDC Core CSIT and also where the DCAE TOSCA files come from. There is also some extra whitespace if you are feeling bored ;-)",
